sanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">多次违反合同以及在SNS上进行误导性和虚假的陈述和行为</a></em>”，它已终止与Seren Ryugetsu的合同。此外，该公司还受到海外VTuber观众和粉丝的激烈批评，其中<a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-announced-minor-financial-impact-from-nijisanji-en-new-selen-tatsuki-terminated/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">IR公告称<em>“对业绩的影响极小</em>”。</a></p><p>据称是Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声优模特的VTuber <strong>Dokibird</strong>的订阅人数自2月5日以来一直在迅速增加，截至2月8日20:45，已达到约418,000人。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="VpBzZ2dwzu"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/selen-tatsuki-supposed-actor-vtuber-dokibird-has-been-return-streaming-127300-watched/">约127,300人观看了VTuber Dokibird的“回归广播”，该广播被认为是Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声音模型。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“约127,300人观看了VTuber Dokibird的《Return Broadcast》，据称该节目是Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声优” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/selen-tatsuki-supposed-actor-vtuber-dokibird-has-been-return-streaming-127300-watched/embed/#?secret=KUJw0SdkWk#?secret=VpBzZ2dwzu" data-secret="VpBzZ2dwzu" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><div class="nkduf65c5d986ec2fb" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
